2. Scalability:
   - Design the application architecture for easy scaling
   - Build easy to maintain and beautifully styled separate components, with useful comments throughout to help engineers scale as product grows.
   - use best practices for structuring the project
   - use engineering judgement to make the project as scalable as possible, while also being easy to understand and maintain

When implementing this smart contract voting / learning application, focus on creating a robust, user-friendly, beautiful solution that showcases your expertise in smart contract based application systems, elegant Tailwind Styling, and full-stack development.